ective way to access the information I need. I want to ensure I gather all the relevant data before proceeding, so this exploration seems like a crucial step. Alright, let’s dive in and see what I can discover!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_028468b01d3bc46e016a40a2cf2410819496c244b4767960e0\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQKLjXdg5EEewKzq0ved4Fnza760TME6Gqug9ebXo3Dw5CGpzIQepy4P3kVi8iaU6NzZtQdNZRaysMN8NDxe-12ao6qqFMOuGU7XdPmj45rkKIZhfDQrMW_91wsxm9XGPCUWUHBAzkCxySuM23lmqlF2XDY6VZZh2_x8tz8X1m6-qoNbMUx2oIM-YJO2ktGHmokTOTdnZE-tkJcCkghoAxF1gC-irWSDi90FDMLokl8NXc8DPEb-_JOcZbGGxAIIcWRFRpCs1Xq08ujDFn0dOhERAA4oJ5V_Ef5N8-ojqoFGY4G_liXyHRhVzwkCYgSgO65aX_ODMYRGR6utDLoxJe0DHfQtpGG2J7BiCOjHzO5kTBrWc-Fu9aXJJyuDGJbuu7Ai5t02D_kaI_pkPRW7NZFIH9xWFdyZv2n2WLC8qQOC9hIlBRSehHgftDiPI8XYcVyySXP0wwtVDhqdcu4ZrnOHiyKzlYywiLgy4KJkxpT3O2btMPYHX5C_FOdWsjcyBToQCgW3Lak9xbCHQUBgGv8K_lLS4SilpVJMquoZudawPzJzvxEq_hFu5DjO3G-MEnd8BO-dkfcW-TBN8ikbT7S6u4_-I7bNBLMbo9CSFsLZSMdgagJ1BPAzELwqLA8Edl_bqI_lWEWQ3fnEfDGIBaTKT1i9rFs7C5hlgp3vJBEJKOU-lJeQfJ3mHhHORhgGpvSbTCxwW0aJcYcvWds_BGK2GM6ILEn9kHz0JRutjmzojWmhI1agLIHKosuO8IXZ9Mlv4YRpAzaWtQ-H809vhxooj_x1hKGUREiU-Pkp-EgBvRSP2kpdv4OjyitVjRCpTq2NZftqgcpnBFrIdNh17MRbpxhUa-qR88USdQ7bgF7Mmx4g3X8EKEl44J3cZTJr5yP0OW703tJJamf_a6M5O7af3UvqNjEqN2oSziEhml9VZgDkwdxARxJGl9k2On5GNdwX0FLJh1DuO2LIOBFln-CNiN435QszyEFXKWWXgF0AgCTh-H3fOKmpcIiK1-LLbaAXLzYqLnrdSBlRg9P4ZSgOHlkaQl-EJucCiCjvJ4fYo32VQgMLJ8PEKqXCuaRiZPIJxmLdjC-cdybql1wT3-2l26HbSHnZj7jOQmZdCSGrpfNGsrQDa-qlv3axQfI1i5ojULMls8yZ7jDkvgPI9eJ2FiU8uJOt1GKrf-K1ulf0khsR9YOQYMECniHS3FDlI1-AVqMtjfDkdjM4WU4oy1jFNUTOadzLNH5VnIrDWofXF7CLfBslUJ3AqCLM9xtEEph1xP3bE_tuyoac3YDvYWvnvQHCs2lRWuj3Ih4KO8KZzY1xmW7PaTzHdkWZIVBe3CTuczZceD4TuZpFTM9gYEhHKMj-Lb97C23Z0qWKULSGCpOWh6ylHUTkLinpX3YNoJyHRvPIcVXNvxxADKgaXfHdCU3vrAKGGtVEP2aHO8TOmQOKzNvtPNb33CvZ_-uehJjzabmg61OaD6h8iopLzUaRkIV3mmHZmYBy6bS8lHVdBdzNyFqCgV6tHCqSFcnxF-5hg0kBwLKBfA4DIJyKccNfh1bKUQ-3936MiDR-klWg0ql1ENl-8wp5ZEvTmdeZ26Fp3qZZbWD1Vq3pzkTiCzGGVWsTse